README Explanation for Unity Build

So far there is an XR/VR dev toolkit that controls the camera (unity's built in packages for XR development.)
There is a mouse looker program that allows you to move the camera/screen around for demo purposes. First build in Build folder.

Inverted sphere with material and render texture (the render texture in question is the video player) which allows you to view the video from inside.

BUILDS ARE IN THE BUILD FOLDER

